  "keyFeatures": [
    "Semantic operators for LLM-powered data transformations (extract, classify, map, join, reduce)",
    "PySpark-inspired DataFrame API with lazy evaluation and query optimization",
    "Native support for unstructured data types (markdown, transcripts, JSON)",
    "Multi-provider LLM support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Cohere, OpenRouter)",
    "Automatic batch optimization and rate limiting for API calls",
    "Built-in token counting and cost tracking",
    "MCP server integration for AI assistants",
    "Production-ready with retry logic and error handling"
